:INFO
Choose Your Base
Wine (red, white, or rose), dry hard cider, or flat beer all work well. Avoid anything \
with artificial sweeteners or preservatives as these will kill your bacteria. Leftover \
wine that is a week or two old is perfect and already starting the process on

