:INFO
Inoculate With a Mother
Pour your base liquid into a wide-mouth jar or crock (wide opening = more oxygen surface \
= faster conversion). Add 20 percent raw apple cider vinegar with the mother, or use a \
dedicated vinegar mother from a brewing supplier. Cover with cheesecloth held

:PATH
Wait, Taste, and Bottle
A rubbery disc (the mother) will form on the surface within 1 to 2 weeks.
|
:INFO
Wait, Taste, and Bottle
A rubbery disc (the mother) will form on the surface within 1 to 2 weeks. Do not disturb \
it. Taste weekly with a clean spoon dipped in below the mother. The vinegar is ready \
when it smells sharp and clean and tastes fully sour with no sweetness. Bottle

:PATH
