|
:INFO
Save Your Mother
Once the vinegar is done, remove the mother and store it in a small jar with a little \
finished vinegar in the fridge. Use it to start your next batch immediately. A healthy \
mother can last indefinitely when fed regularly with fresh alcohol.

:NOTE
Surface Area Is Everything
The main variable you can control is the width of your vessel. A wide \
crock or a standard canning jar with the widest mouth you own will \
outperform a narrow bottle every time. More surface means more oxygen \
contact, which means faster, cleaner conversion.

